{"tid":1529692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔怕死唔夠做　要調整心態","createTime":"2019-09-01T19:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T20:37:55.000Z","uid":21410,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d81878969890e7a2d7c2e93c0b1e6ed8cadf1b4f","tid":1529692,"uid":21410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:36:01.000Z","msg":"好多人　唔怕死　　　<br />\n但得好少人出到手　<br />\n<br />\n其實蓄龍／防暴贏　唔係特別好打　　唔係因為gear勁　<br />\n而係　佢地心態上贏　大家而家係驚左佢　所以唔敢面對<br />\n所以要贏人　先要放低兵賊心態　<br />\n<br />\n佢地只不過係一個人　<br />\n佢地都會怕死　可能怕過我地　<br />\n只不過佢地有一個心態　就係　今日出黎打甲由<br />\n<br />\n只要大家有　今日我要打蓄龍　　<br />\n最好大家要去到有　唔好同我爭　呢個我既心態<br />\n蓄龍／防暴　唔係咁可怕<br />\n<br />\n佢地係有操開　又　有Ｇｅａｒ　<br />\n我地夠有人多呢個優勢　<br />\n幾勁　幾好裝都好　　得一對手你估佢葉問呀？<br />\n<br />\n平均一隊先得１０幾人　　我地圍返佢爭住打都仲得　<br />\n改變到心態既話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　　"},{"pid":"bfcf64db904446a2f69044a80199638ed3f8a1f6","tid":1529692,"uid":115712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc2d4d53148c13656ace3516bd48ba3ba62694a","tid":1529692,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:40:03.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大